org.openwms.common.location

Class Location

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ameba.integration.jpa.BaseEntity
      • org.openwms.common.location.Location
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, org.ameba.integration.TypedEntity<Long>

    @Entity
public class Location
extends org.ameba.integration.jpa.BaseEntity
implements Serializable
    A Location, represents a physical or virtual place in a warehouse. Could be something like a storage location in the stock or a location on a conveyor. Error locations can be modeled with a Location entity, too. Multiple Locations are grouped to a LocationGroup.
    Since:
    0.1
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Heiko Scherrer
    See Also:
    LocationGroup, Serialized Form
